quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  34,46,"Sọ pé: “Ohun kan ṣoṣo ni mò ń ṣe wáàsí rẹ̀ fun yín pé, ẹ dúró nítorí ti Allāhu ní méjì àti ní ẹyọ kọ̀ọ̀kan. Lẹ́yìn náà, kí ẹ ronú jinlẹ̀. Kò sí àlùjànnú kan lára ẹni yín. Kò sì jẹ́ kiní kan bí kò ṣe olùkìlọ̀ fun yín ṣíwájú ìyà líle kan.”"
  34,47,"Sọ pé: “Èmi kò bi yín léèrè owó-ọ̀yà kan, ẹ̀yin lẹ kúkú lowó yín. Kò sí owó ọ̀yà mi (lọ́dọ̀ ẹnì kan) àfi lọ́dọ̀ Allāhu. Òun sì ni Arínú-róde gbogbo n̄ǹkan.”"
  34,48,"Sọ pé: “Dájúdájú Olúwa mi, Onímọ̀-ìkọ̀kọ̀ l’Ó ń mú òdodo wá.”"
  34,49,"Sọ pé: “Òdodo ti dé. Irọ́ (èṣù) kò lè mú n̄ǹkan bẹ, kò sì lè dá n̄ǹkan padà (lẹ́yìn tó ti kú).”"
  34,50,"Sọ pé: “Tí mo bá ṣìnà, mo ṣìnà fún ẹ̀mí ara mi ni. Tí mo bá sì mọ̀nà, nípa ohun tí Olúwa mi fi ránṣẹ́ sì mi ní ìmísí ni. Dájúdájú Òun ni Olùgbọ́, Alásùn-únmọ́ ẹ̀dá.”"
  34,51,"Tí ó bá jẹ́ pé o lè rí (ẹ̀sín wọn ni) nígbà tí ẹ̀rù bá dé bá wọn (ní Ọjọ́ Àjíǹde, o máa rí i pé), kò níí sí ìmóríbọ́ kan (fún wọn). A sì máa gbá wọn mú láti àyè t’ó súnmọ́"
  34,52,"Wọn yóò wí pé: “A gbàgbọ́ nínú (al-Ƙur’ān báyìí).” Báwo ni ọwọ́ wọn ṣe lè tẹ ìgbàgbọ́ òdodo láti àyè t’ó jìnnà (ìyẹn, ọ̀run).”"
  34,53,"Wọ́n kúkú ti ṣàì gbàgbọ́ nínú rẹ̀ ṣíwájú (nílé ayé). Wọ́n sì ń sọ̀rọ̀ nípa ìkọ̀kọ̀ láti àyè t’ó jìnnà (ìyẹn, ilé ayé)"
  34,54,A sì fi gàgá sí ààrin àwọn àti ohun tí wọ́n ń ṣojú kòkòrò rẹ̀ gẹ́gẹ́ bí A ti ṣe fún àwọn ẹgbẹ́ wọn ní ìṣáájú. Dájúdájú wọ́n wà nínú iyèméjì t’ó gbópọn (nípa Ọjọ́ Àjíǹde)